How to use this for DRISHTI quickly
When you design in Antigravity / Django templates:

Base template:

CPGRAMS-style header with DRISHTI branding.

Top horizontal menu with the same item order: Home, Lodge Complaint, Track Status, Reminder/Clarification, Rate Resolution, Help, Login.
â€‹

No heavy sidebars on public pages:

CPGRAMS mainly uses full-width content with top navigation, not complex sidebars for citizens.
â€‹

Use sidebar only on officer/admin dashboards if you want extra modern structure.

Form-first design:

Every important action is a clean form with a plain label + input + mandatory field star.

Place â€œSubmitâ€ and â€œResetâ€ buttons clearly, like in CPENGRAMS forms.
â€‹

